1
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,220
Yuwen Ying.

2
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,759
Vava has sent the approximate

3
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,440
coordinates of the Glass Frog analyzed by AI

4
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,560
to your phone.

5
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,479
The rest is up to you.

6
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,400
Speak.

7
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,200
I found the thing

8
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,480
you wanted.

9
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,079
I'll bring it back to you.

10
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,240
Besides,

11
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:34,079
I won't have to waste any more time

12
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,300
with that old man, Professor Wei.

13
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,180
No need for now.

14
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,290
It's not the right time yet.

15
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,400
Keep the items

16
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,520
on your side.

17
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,440
That's not what we agreed on.

18
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,640
I don't want just a Copper Frog.

19
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,320
I want Buluotuo's Tear.

20
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:51,880
You must take that Copper Frog,

21
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:53,600
return to the Professor,

22
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,280
and help him find

23
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,560
Buluotuo's Tear.

24
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,480
Is that clear?

25
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,200
Whether it's Aya or the Professor,

26
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,080
whoever gets Buluotuo's Tear,

27
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,000
it belongs to me.

28
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,220
Professor,

29
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,680
it worked.

30
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,520
Let me see.

31
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,040
This is wonderful.

32
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,560
The AI has successfully read

33
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,520
all the information on the Liuli Frog.

34
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,079
We now have

35
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,880
a clue to the second Bronze Frog.

36
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:52,880
I knew

37
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,360
I would succeed.

38
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,040
Liu Yu.

39
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,600
Where did Liu Yu go?

40
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:01,200
Liu Yu said he went to the restroom

41
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:03,280
and asked me to hold his spot.

42
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:04,700
Professor,

43
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,620
the Liuli Frog is gone too.

44
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:00,920
Liu Yu,

45
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,610
get out here!

46
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,600
Liu Yu, get out here!

47
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,360
Liu Yu!

48
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:09,940
Professor Wei.

49
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,780
My dear Comrade Wei Mingyuan.

50
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,760
This letter must have been

51
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,960
found by Yu Wenying.

52
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,680
Your glasses

53
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,920
should have been replaced long ago.

54
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,880
Don't just spend your money on research.

55
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,280
You need to treat yourself better.

56
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,000
By the time you read this letter,

57
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,880
I'll be gone.

58
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,240
I'm borrowing that Liuli Frog for a bit.

59
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,970
I'm definitely not selling it.

60
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,140
I just want to find my parents.

61
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,880
The Copper Frog is the only clue to Buluotuo's Tears.

62
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:37,409
It's also the only clue to finding my parents.

63
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,680
You old...

64
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,320
Forget it.

65
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,480
We're saying goodbye,

66
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,140
so I won't say anything nasty.

67
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,240
You insisted on taking my parents on an adventure,

68
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,720
making me an orphan.

69
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:51,120
You've wronged me in so many ways.

70
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,920
I couldn't even begin to list them all.

71
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,180
When I find my parents,

72
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,480
I'll forgive you.

73
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,640
Then,

74
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,720
I'll treat you to dinner.

75
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,980
Let's leave it at that.

76
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,620
So for all these years,

77
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,800
you've been blaming me.

78
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,480
I'm the one who failed all of you.
